Insider Activity


Individual




R. Brad Oates



Mr. R. B. Oates is Independent Director at CIT Group, Inc., Chairman & Managing Partner at Stone Advisors LP, Managing Director & Operating Partner at Z Capital Group LLC and Operational Partner at Z Capital Partners LLC . He is on the Board of Directors at Neways Enterprises, Inc., CIT Group, Inc., CIT Bank NA (Utah) and Gearingstone LLC. Mr. Oates was previously employed as President & Chief Operating Officer by Bluebonnet Savings Bank, FSB, Executive Vice President by Stone Holdings, Inc., and Chairman by NFC Global LLC. He also served on the board at eBureau LLC. He received his graduate degree from Brigham Young University.



